content.text:
During this experiment, you will view a sequence of items 
which will appear one at a time on the screen.
Some of these items will be completely NEW items that you
have not seen before within the experiment.
Other items will be OLD - items that are identical to those
you have previously seen.
Other items will be SIMILAR, but not exactly the same,
as items you have previously seen.

As each item appears, you will press a key to indicate
if the item is OLD (J), SIMILAR (K), or NEW (L)

Press a key to begin
